      <title>促成德国统一的朔伊布勒去世，享年 81 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/schaeuble-who-helped-forge-german-reunification-dies-at-81</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔夫冈·朔伊布勒 (Wolfgang Schaeuble) 去世了，他曾帮助促成德国统一，但在 2000 年被安吉拉·默克尔 (Angela Merkel) 推翻党内领导地位，近十年后又在欧元危机期间重新出任财政部长。他81岁了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/schaeuble-who-helped-forge-german-reunification-dies-at-81</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 08:57:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统否决后提出加薪计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/polish-president-proposes-wage-increase-plan-after-veto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总统安杰伊·杜达 (Andrzej Duda) 在因对公共媒体提供额外援助的争执中否决了政府的法案后，提出了明年提高教师和其他公共部门工作人员工资的立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/polish-president-proposes-wage-increase-plan-after-veto</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 08:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
